30:30.066 --> 30:34.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VLADIMIR KARA-MURZA: And I
started suddenly feeling really,
really sick, and within a

30:34.000 --> 30:39.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
