31:40.133 --> 31:44.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Denis Voronenkov was a pro-Putin
lawmaker who defected to
Ukraine and became a Putin

31:44.766 --> 31:46.833 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
