32:17.600 --> 32:20.900 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But he'd also been an
investigator who uncovered
corruption in the Russian
intelligence agency,

32:20.900 --> 32:22.100 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
the FSB.

32:22.100 --> 32:23.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Who do you think
killed your husband?

32:23.366 --> 32:26.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
MARIA MAKSAKOVA: He
had certain enemies.

32:26.266 --> 32:28.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And these enemies
