everything, positions.

32:43.566 --> 32:45.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that was something that
they would not let him do.

32:45.933 --> 32:48.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Russia calls
her claim a fabrication.

32:48.900 --> 32:50.966 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But his death fits a pattern.

32:50.966 --> 32:54.166 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A once-loyal family member
becomes an outspoken
opponent and ends up dead.

32:54.166 --> 32:57.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MASHA GESSEN, Author/Activist:
A mafia family, you can be born
into, you can be adopted into

32:57.366 --> 32:58.366 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

32:58.366 --> 33:00.466 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You can't leave it voluntarily.

33:00.466 --> 33:03.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
People who have tried to leave
the Putin family voluntarily
have not fared very well.

33:03.900 --> 33:08.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Masha Gessen is a
Russian journalist, author, and
prolific anti-Putin activist.

33:08.866 --> 33:12.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
