need for mobilization.

33:52.233 --> 33:55.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
To have mobilization,
you need to have enemies.

33:55.300 --> 34:00.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You can have LGBT people as
enemies today, and then you
can have Americans tomorrow,

34:00.333 --> 34:04.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
and keep the LGBT people in
your back pocket and then pull
them out when you need them

34:04.333 --> 34:06.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
